d=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F41406553&amp;rft.aulast=Thomas&amp;rft.aufirst=Roger+G.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AG.+E.+Ferguson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation journal\">Arhin, Kwame (1985). \"George Ekem Ferguson of the Gold Coast Colony, 1864-1897\". <i>Research Reports of the African Studies Centre</i>. Leiden (25).</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Research+Reports+of+the+African+Studies+Centre&amp;rft.atitle=George+Ekem+Ferguson+of+the+Gold+Coast+Colony%2C+1864-1897&amp;rft.issue=25&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.aulast=Arhin&amp;rft.aufirst=Kwame&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AG.+E.+Ferguson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation journal\">Dumett, Raymond E; Arhin, Kwame (1975). \"Review of The Papers of George Ekem Ferguson: A Fanti Official of the Government of the Gold Coast, 1890-1897 by Kwame Arhin\". <i>The International Journal of African Historical Studies</i>. The International Journal of African Historical Studies, Vol. 8, No. 4. <b>8</b> (4). <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.2307/216721\">10.2307/216721</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/JSTOR\" title=\"JSTOR\">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.jstor.org/stable/216721\">216721</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+International+Journal+of+African+Historical+Studies&amp;rft.atitle=Review+of+The+Papers+of+George+Ekem+Ferguson%3A+A+Fanti+Official+of+the+Government+of+the+Gold+Coast%2C+1890-1897+by+Kwame+Arhin&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.date=1975&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F216721&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F216721&amp;rft.aulast=Dumett&amp;rft.aufirst=Raymond+E&amp;rft.au=Arhin%2C+Kwame&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AG.+E.+Ferguson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation journal\">Thomas, R. (1972). \"George Ekem Ferguson: Civil Servant Extraordinary\". <i>Transactions of the Historical society of Ghana</i>. <b>13</b> (2).</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Transactions+of+the+Historical+society+of+Ghana&amp;rft.atitle=George+Ekem+Ferguson%3A+Civil+Servant+Extraordinary&amp;rft.volume=13&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.date=1972&amp;rft.aulast=Thomas&amp;rft.aufirst=R.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AG.+E.+Ferguson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=G._E._Ferguson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070930200322/http://www.archimedes.free-online.co.uk/ferguson.jpg\">Depiction of Ferguson</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=G._E._Ferguson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\">Ferguson, George Ekem (1974).  <a href=\"/wiki/Kwame_Arhin\" title=\"Kwame Arhin\">Kwame Arhin</a>, ed. <i>The Papers of George Ekem Ferguson: A Fanti Official of the Government of the Gold Coast, 1890-1897</i>. African Social Research Documents, Vol. 7. Leiden: <a href=\"/wiki/Afrika-Studiecentrum,_Leiden\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Afrika-Studiecentrum, Leiden\">African Studies Centre</a>. p.&#160;178.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Papers+of+George+Ekem+Ferguson%3A+A+Fanti+Official+of+the+Government+of+the+Gold+Coast%2C+1890-1897&amp;rft.place=Leiden&amp;rft.series=African+Social+Research+Documents%2C+Vol.+7&amp;rft.pages=178&amp;rft.pub=African+Studies+Centre&amp;rft.date=1974&amp;rft.aulast=Ferguson&amp;rft.aufirst=George+Ekem&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AG.+E.+Ferguson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q5512212&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th id=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q5512212&amp;#124;Edit_this_at_Wikidata\" scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Help:Authority_control\" title=\"Help:Authority control\">Authority control</a> <a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q5512212\" title=\"Edit this at Wikidata\"><img alt=\"Edit this at Wikidata\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/10px-Blue_pencil.svg.png\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" style=\"vertical-align: text-top\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/15px-Blue_pencil.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikip